{"id":277311,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/墙外楼-看不见的北京：连续2天六级严重污染/","date":"2013-02-01T04:31:15Z","modified":"2013-02-01T04:31:15Z","title":"墙外楼 | 看不见的北京：连续2天六级严重污染","content":"<p><p>1月29日，北京深陷雾霾包围，这已经是1月以来雾霾第四次侵扰京城。雾霾使得北京成为了“看不见的城市”。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.letscorp.net/lynn/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/900x600_8MFD90C600AN0001.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.letscorp.net/lynn/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/900x600_8MFD90C600AN0001.jpg\" alt=\"900x600_8MFD90C600AN0001\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n<p>醒来后，所有人都去寻找那座城市。没有找到城市，那些人却会聚到了一起，于是，大家决定建造一座梦境中的城市。  卡尔维诺《看不见的城市》  封面摄影/Getty/Feng Li</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.letscorp.net/lynn/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/900x600_8MFD64F200AN0001.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.letscorp.net/lynn/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/900x600_8MFD64F200AN0001.jpg\" alt=\"900x600_8MFD64F200AN0001\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n<p>1月29日，天安门广场，北京深陷雾霾包围，这已经是1月以来雾霾第四次侵扰京城。Getty/Feng Li</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.letscorp.net/lynn/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/900x600_8MFD61F700AN0001.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.letscorp.net/lynn/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/900x600_8MFD61F700AN0001.jpg\" alt=\"900x600_8MFD61F700AN0001\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n<p>1月16日，北京，被薄雾覆盖的故宫博物院。Getty/Feng Li</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.letscorp.net/lynn/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/900x600_8MFD616400AN0001.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.letscorp.net/lynn/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/900x600_8MFD616400AN0001.jpg\" alt=\"900x600_8MFD616400AN0001\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n<p>1月16日，北京，被薄雾覆盖的故宫博物院。Getty/Feng Li</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.letscorp.net/lynn/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/900x600_8MFD651000AN0001.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.letscorp.net/lynn/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/900x600_8MFD651000AN0001.jpg\" alt=\"900x600_8MFD651000AN0001\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" /></a></p>\n<p>1月29日，北京发布大雾黄色预警，图为大雾下降落的航班。CFP/TAORAN</p>\n<p>